			<h3>About</h3>
			<p>
				d3pie is a simple, highly configurable script built on <a href="http://d3js.org/" target="_blank">d3.js</a>
				for creating simple, attractive pie charts. It's free, open source, and found on
				<a href="https://github.com/benkeen/d3pie">github</a>.
			</p>
			<p>
				To get started, check out the <a href="#generator" class="selectPage" data-toggle="tab">generator</a> -
				it lets you see some examples, and construct and fine-tune your own pie charts via a simple UI. For further
				info on the script, visit the <a href="#docs" class="selectPage" data-toggle="tab">documentation</a>. Enjoy!
			</p>

			<h3 style="margin-top:25px">Browser Support</h3>
			<p>
				All modern browsers: Chrome, Firefox, Safari, IE9 and up.
			</p>
		</div>
