		</div>
		<div class="col-lg-4 col3">
			<p>
				Configuration options include:
			</p>
			<ul class="aboutPageList">
				<li>Pie / donut charts</li>
				<li>Title, subtitle, footer text and control over placement</li>
				<li>Inner and outer labels; choice of what data appears in each</li>
				<li>Automatic percentage calculations</li>
				<li>Unlimited data set size</li>
				<li>Full control over font, font sizes, colors</li>
				<li>Segment colors</li>
				<li>Small segment grouping</li>
				<li>Background color / transparency</li>
				<li>Load, mouseover and click effects</li>
				<li>Callbacks for click, mouseover, mouseout events</li>
				<li>API for refreshing and recreating pie dynamically</li>
				<li>Control over pie chart padding, pie chart x/y offsets</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
